vofi-specific configuration options
======================================

Build Process
-------------

1. ./configure --prefix=/path/to/vofi/install

2. make all

3. make check
   (optional, runs the example programs and unit tests when possible)
   
4. make install


METHODS
-------

to be completed


Dependencies
============

Requirements
------------

vofi has no required dependencies other than a reasonably modern C, Fortran
& C++ compiler.  

